{"tid":783043,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人攝野喺牙幾日先了翻出來?","createTime":"2018-08-17T09:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T08:20:13.000Z","uid":113821,"like":8,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6b78259f70a89ee545bf757839bf253c7da2699c","tid":783043,"uid":113821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"本人鵬牙最入有個凹窩，比牙肉遮住刷牙都未必刷到<br />\n幾日前食舊肉，今日先發現攝左D碎喺個窩到，然後了翻出來。<br />\n頭先捏碎舊臭肉來聞，陣味真喺畢生難忘，仲臭過白色珍珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後再食翻，酸酸地真喺好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無爸打試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25a2c4750ae4bfaac16521b602fe84685d9850d","tid":783043,"uid":113821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e89bebd05ea34e4d0887647340489991d418923","tid":783043,"uid":113821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28eae34e55885dfa6a3f80108b4a5ab35634162e","tid":783043,"uid":113821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8204dd92d8f09893d30172b7b7cfb6252dd12008","tid":783043,"uid":84314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:06:13.000Z","msg":"咁都唔發炎算你好彩"},{"pid":"6f5c73f1301fccb21cb32a4a1dacca16aa0fb3c6","tid":783043,"uid":3093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"水牙線幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkg